description: Try this gluten-free air-fryer chicken schnitzel recipe. Serve these crispy bite-sized chicken pieces with a spicy mayonnaise.
name: Gluten-Free Air-Fryer Chicken Schnitzel Bites Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 0.5 cup Free From Gluten plain flour

recipeInstructions.text: Meanwhile, combine mayonnaise with sriracha in a small bowl. Season with pepper. Garnish chicken with extra parsley, then serve with mayonnaise mixture and lemon.
